over time, why are we here?

00:31:06.390 --> 00:31:10.899
Why is anything complex and
intricate and organized exist

00:31:10.899 --> 00:31:11.565
in the universe?

00:31:11.565 --> 00:31:13.240
This is another good
question to which

00:31:13.240 --> 00:31:15.776
we don't know the
complete answer,

00:31:15.776 --> 00:31:17.150
but it's interesting
